WEBVTT

00:00:01.435 --> 00:00:04.126
How many of you are tired

00:00:04.674 --> 00:00:09.135
of seeing celebrities adopting kids
from the African continent?

00:00:09.159 --> 00:00:10.738
(Laughter)

00:00:12.342 --> 00:00:14.696
Well, it's not all that bad.

00:00:16.573 --> 00:00:17.941
I was adopted.

00:00:19.451 --> 00:00:22.153
I grew up in rural Uganda,

00:00:23.495 --> 00:00:26.263
lost both my parents
when I was very, very young.

